trans-unit.source: Provides a component editor for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DataBindings*> collection of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en komponent redigeringsprogrammet for den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DataBindings*>samling av den tilknyttede <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DataBindings*>

trans-unit.source: The MenuBindingsEditor class provides a user interface for editing the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemBinding> elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DataBindings%2A> collection within the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Klassen MenuBindingsEditor gir et brukergrensesnitt for redigering av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemBinding>elementer i den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DataBindings%2A>samling i den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DataBindings%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemBinding>

trans-unit.source: The MenuBindingsEditor object is invoked by selecting the ellipsis (**…**) button on the **DataBindings** property in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer, or by choosing **Edit Menu Items** from the **Common Tasks** context menu on the control.
trans-unit.target: Objektet MenuBindingsEditor aktiveres ved å velge ellipsen (**... **)-knappen på den **databindinger** egenskap i den **Egenskaper** rutenett for den visuelle utformeren, eller ved å velge **Rediger menyelementer** fra den **vanlige oppgaver** hurtigmenyen kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor.EditValue%2A> method edits the values of the data bindings collection of the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor.EditValue%2A>metoden redigerer verdiene for bindinger datainnsamlingen for den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor.EditValue%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor.GetEditStyle%2A> method gets the editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor.GetEditStyle%2A>metoden henter redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor.GetEditStyle%2A>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The .NET Framework internally constructs a new instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor> class when you select the ellipsis (**…**) button on the **DataBindings** property in the **Properties** grid of the visual designer, or by choosing **Edit Menu Items** from the **Common Tasks** context menu on the control, when designing the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: .NET Framework internt bygger en ny forekomst av klassen <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor>Når du velger ellipsen (**... **)-knappen på den **databindinger** egenskap i den **Egenskaper** rutenett for den visuelle utformeren, eller ved å velge **Rediger menyelementer** fra den **vanlige oppgaver** hurtigmenyen kontrollen, når du utformer den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuBindingsEditor>

trans-unit.source: Edits the value of the data bindings collection of the associated <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"></xref> control.
trans-unit.target: Redigerer bindinger datainnsamlingen for den tilknyttede verdien <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu"> </xref> kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The EditValue method extracts the associated <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control and the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object that is associated with that control from the `context` parameter.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EditValue trekker ut den tilknyttede <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontrollen og <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>objektet som er forbundet med denne kontrollen fra den `context` parameteren.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: Then the EditValue method calls back on the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner> object to display an editing dialog box that is used to edit the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemBindingCollection> collection of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: Metoden EditValue kaller deretter tilbake på den <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>objektet til å vise en redigering dialogboks som brukes til å redigere den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemBindingCollection>samling av <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>kontroll.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.MenuItemBindingCollection> </xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.MenuDesigner>

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> interface that is used to acquire context information.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> grensesnitt som brukes til å hente informasjon om sikkerhetskontekst.

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref:System.IServiceProvider> interface, through which editing services can be obtained.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref:System.IServiceProvider>grensesnitt som redigering services kan hentes.</xref:System.IServiceProvider>

trans-unit.source: The object to edit the value for.
trans-unit.target: Objektet til å redigere verdien for.

trans-unit.source: The new value; otherwise, if the value of the object has not changed, value unchanged.
trans-unit.target: Den nye value ; Ellers hvis verdien for objektet ikke er endret, value uendret.

trans-unit.source: Gets the editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Henter redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.

trans-unit.source: The GetEditStyle method always returns the <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle> value, which indicates that the editor user interface (UI) is a modal dialog box.
trans-unit.target: Metoden GetEditStyle returnerer alltid den <xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>-verdi som angir at redigeringsprogrammet-brukergrensesnittet (UI) er en modal dialogboks.</xref:System.Drawing.Design.UITypeEditorEditStyle>

trans-unit.source: An object implementing the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"></xref> interface that indicates the context of the object being edited.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som implementerer den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ITypeDescriptorContext"> </xref> grensesnitt som angir konteksten for objektet som redigeres.

trans-unit.source: The editing style that is associated with this editor.
trans-unit.target: Redigering stilen som er knyttet til dette redigeringsprogrammet.
